title: Marvel's Dr. Strange TV Pilot (1978)
description: Let loose the hoary hosts of Hoggoth, sit back, and enjoy this decidedly lo-fi, live action television adaptation of the Sorcerer Supreme.  The special effects are laughable, and comic purists may find fault with certain story elements, but it's actually a decent movie.  Certainly not the best comic adaptation ever made, but it does harmonize well with the Incredible Hulk series also running on CBS during the same time frame. Enjoy!
